snippet.title: Monster Hunter: World - PS4 Gameplay Interview | E3 2017
snippet.description:
Monster Hunter is coming back to PS4, and we've got brand new gameplay as well as first details. Learn more about Monster Hunter: Worlds robust multiplayer and new features from our live interview at E3 2017.
